      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Debian系Linux安装N卡驱动参考这篇&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.if-not-true-then-false.com/2021/debian-ubuntu-linux-mint-nvidia-guide/&#34;&gt;博客&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
